		"_postman_id": "smart-city-hub-api-2024",
		"name": "Smart City Hub API",
		"description": "Complete API collection for Smart City Hub - Urban Incident Management Platform.\n\n## Authentication\nMost endpoints require JWT Bearer Authentication. First register/login to get tokens, then set the `{{accessToken}}` variable.\n\n## Roles\n- **ROLE_USER**: Citizens who can report incidents\n- **ROLE_AGENT**: Municipal agents who handle incidents\n- **ROLE_SUPERVISOR**: Supervisors who manage agents\n- **ROLE_ADMIN**: Administrators with full access",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
